    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，所以LMS门户是第一个节点。这个内容CDN的判断是一个分支点吗？比如命中缓存和未命中缓存两种情况？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Yes/No分支。命中缓存就直接返回内容，未命中就要去源站或数据库拉取。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我先画出LMS门户指向CDN判断节点，然后分出Yes和No两条线。Yes分支先到CDN节点获取内容。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Yes分支后面还有一步，CDN需要记录访问日志到学生数据库，用于学习行为分析。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加：CDN节点指向学生数据库。接下来从学生数据库返回哪里？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "学生数据库写完后，流程回到CDN，然后CDN把内容最终返回给LMS门户，完成一次资源请求。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，CDN到门户的返回链路已画好。但这里门户节点似乎有两个，我需要确认是同一个门户的不同状态还是？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "是同一个门户，只是表示请求完成后的下一步——门户需要触发成绩同步服务，把这次学习活动的进度更新过去。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "理解了，门户指向GradeSync服务。GradeSync完成后又流向哪里？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "GradeSync需要再次经过CDN，把成绩数据缓存同步到边缘节点，这样教师端能快速查看。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "GradeSync到CDN的连线已添加。CDN之后呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "然后到课堂服务，这是实际推送通知给在线教室的组件，最后回到LMS门户显示更新后的成绩状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "CDN到ClassroomService，再到LMS门户，这条链路完成了。现在回到之前的No分支——CDN缓存未命中的情况。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "No分支直接走到ClassroomService，这里其实是走实时计算路径，不经过缓存，直接查询课堂服务的实时状态返回给门户。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已连接No分支到ClassroomService。不过我发现ClassroomService后面已经连了LMS门户，这样No分支也能自然汇合。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
