      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 22,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已修复E到F的连线。现在完整检查一遍：A门户→B判断→Yes→C→D→E学生库→F→G门户→H门户→I成绩同步→J→K课堂服务→L门户，同时B的No直接到K。结构正确吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
